## Third-Party Acknowledgments

This project integrates with and acknowledges the following services and APIs:

- NASA TEMPO Mission (https://tempo.si.edu/)
- EPA AirNow API (https://www.airnow.gov/)
- Open-Meteo Weather API (https://open-meteo.com/)
- OpenStreetMap Nominatim (https://nominatim.org/)
- Leaflet.js Mapping Library (https://leafletjs.com/)

## Data Attribution

Air quality data is provided by:
- NASA's Tropospheric Emissions: Monitoring of Pollution (TEMPO) mission
- U.S. Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) AirNow program
- Open-Meteo meteorological services

